import {Outlet} from 'react-router-dom';

import Subnavigation from '../layouts/subnavigation'
import SubnavItem from '../layouts/subnavitem'

import styled from 'styled-components'
import '../styles/theme.css'

import JavascriptLogo from '../assets/logo-javascript.svg'
import PythonLogo from '../assets/logo-python.svg'
import RedisLogo from '../assets/logo-redis.svg'
import AppleLogo from '../assets/logo-apple.svg'
import AndroidLogo from '../assets/logo-android.svg'

function Services() {
  return (
    <StyledContainer>
      <Subnavigation title='Services'>
        <SubnavGroup>
          <SubnavItem to='frontend'>Frontend Services</SubnavItem>  
          <SubnavItem to='javascript' src={JavascriptLogo}>Javascript</SubnavItem>
        </SubnavGroup>
        <SubnavGroup>
          <SubnavItem to='backend'>Backend Services</SubnavItem>
          <SubnavItem to='python' src={PythonLogo}>Python</SubnavItem>
          <SubnavItem to='redis' src={RedisLogo}>Redis</SubnavItem>
        </SubnavGroup>
        <SubnavGroup>
        <SubnavItem to='mobile'>Mobile Services</SubnavItem> 
        <SubnavItem to='apple' src={AppleLogo}>iOS</SubnavItem>
        <SubnavItem to='android' src={AndroidLogo}>Android</SubnavItem>
        </SubnavGroup>
      </Subnavigation>
      <Outlet/>
    </StyledContainer>
  )
}

const StyledContainer = styled('div')`
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 200px auto;
`;

const SubnavGroup = styled('div')`
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
`;

export default Services;
